query:
UPDATE `courses` SET `curriculum` = 'Week 1-4: Fundamentals of Algebra
• Variables and expressions
• Linear equations and inequalities
• Systems of equations
• Word problems and applications

Week 5-8: Geometry Essentials
• Angles, triangles, and polygons
• Area and perimeter calculations
• Pythagorean theorem
• Coordinate geometry

Week 9-12: Advanced Topics
• Quadratic equations
• Functions and graphs
• Exponential and logarithmic functions
• Practice tests and review' WHERE `subject` = 'Mathematics' LIMIT 1;
